Subject: drm/amdgpu/gfx9: wait for completion in KIQ init
Git-commit: 2fdde9fa9705cb4df29445c2a4dd241b1e9c03f2
Patch-mainline: v4.13-rc1
References: FATE#326289 FATE#326079 FATE#326049 FATE#322398 FATE#326166

We need to make sure the various init sequences submitted
to KIQ complete before testing the rings.

